thread.title: High school football: Riordan tops Serra to remain unbeaten
thread.title_full: High school football: Riordan tops Serra to remain unbeaten - San Francisco Chronicle

author: Special to The Chronicle
title: High school football: Riordan tops Serra to remain unbeaten
text: In a wild West Catholic Athletic League game, No. 11 Riordan rolled up 621 yards of total offense and turned a 32-29 first-quarter lead into a smashing 66-45 victory over No. 5 Serra on Saturday at City College of San Francisco.
